Sentencas: Anode coking problem of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) when using hydrocarbon fuels has been the major barrier for the practice and commercialization of well-developed high performance SOFC.
Titulo: Direct liquid methanol-fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In this work, based on fuels consideration, we chose liquid methanol as the candidate fuel for SOFC with the configuration of NiO/SDC-SDC-SSC/SDC.
Titulo: Direct liquid methanol-fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: For comparison, traditional fuels, hydrogen and ammonia, were tested.
Titulo: Direct liquid methanol-fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: With methanol as fuel, the maximum power densities were 698, 430 and 223 mW cm(-2) at 650, 600 and 550 degrees C, respectively, which were higher than that with ammonia and lower than that of hydrogen.
Titulo: Direct liquid methanol-fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The electrochemical properties of the cells with the three fuels were investigated by AC impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Direct liquid methanol-fueled solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The long-term stability of the cell with methanol, methane and ethanol were also studied at a constant output voltage of 0.5 V. (c) 2008 Elsevier B.V.
Titulo: Direct liquid methanol-fueled solid oxide fuel cell
